{"type":"text","timestamp":1775844302618,"sessionID":"ses_28772e49effe617laS4xnvcyTz","part":{"id":"prt_d78919406001M6NTzJwmVsaJyi","messageID":"msg_d789187f4001yr8dcp31zAbSaX","sessionID":"ses_28772e49effe617laS4xnvcyTz","type":"text","text":"Created design.md for AR-006 at `sandbox-orchestration/AR-006-sandbox-deletion-lifecycle/design.md`. The document covers:\n\n- **Delete API endpoints**: `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` and `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId`\n- **GarbageCollector**: Background goroutine running every 15s to cleanup idle (15m) and expired (8h) sandboxes\n- **Error handling**: 404 for missing sessions, K8s NotFound treated as success\n- **Testing strategy**: Unit tests for handlers and GC, integration tests for E2E deletion\n- **Integration**: Store interface, SandboxReconciler watcher cleanup","time":{"start":1775844302616,"end":1775844302616}}}
